Name: Kilemol
About the game: Kill spaceships and shooter enemies with the weapons at your disposal. Be careful not to run out of ammunition though. The stronger the weapon, the less ammunition it has. Try to destroy the spawn capsules before killing the enemies for your own sake. Features: - 50 dynamic levels; - 5 types of enemies; - 5 types of weapons; - Frenetic gameplay;
